high_descs: Turn right and walk to the right side of the sink.
Take the towel on the wall of of the towel rack.
Turn left and walk to the toilet.
Put the towel on top of the toilet tank.
Turn around and face the sink.
Take the towel on the left off the towel rack.
Turn around and face the toilet.
Place the towel on the toilet behind the other towel.
anns.task_desc: Place two towels on a toilet.

high_descs: Move to the towel rack right of the sink.
Pick up the towel from the rack.
Bring the towel to the toilet.
Place the towel standing on the toilet tank lid.
Move to the sink.
Pick up the towel to the left of the sink.
Bring the towel to the toilet.
Place the towel next to the other towel on the toilet tank lid.
anns.task_desc: Put two towels on the toilet tank lid.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk over to the towel on the wall
Pick up the towel hanging on the wall
Turn around and walk over to the toilet on your right
Place the towel above the toilet
Turn around and go to the left sink
Pick up the towel in front of you
Turn around again, and look at the toilet
Place the towel behind the other towel, above the toilet
anns.task_desc: Place two towels above the toilet
